	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scriberem copiosius de exitu comitiorum <placeName ref="l760" cert="high">Salodurensium</placeName>, nisi existimarem d. a <persName type="auto_name">Scharteres</persName>, qui iis interfuit, et tibi et inprimis illustrissimo principi <placeName type="auto_name">Condensi</placeName> iam ordine omnia exposuisse.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nostri iam agunt de mittenda in Galliam legatione.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Prius tamen visum est in comitiis congregatis mittendum esse ad <placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtembergensem</placeName> et percontandum, qua via principes Germani suos sint legatos missuri, si forte 5 cantonum legati, nempe Tigurinorum; <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l41" cert="high">Bernatum</placeName>, <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronensium</placeName>, <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basiliensium</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l441" cert="high">Schaffhusianorum</placeName> illis se coniungerent.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego hic maxime sol[l]icitus sum, ut qui experientia doctus recordor, quantum in nostro illi infelici bello ante annos 30 gesto nobis et synceritati religionis compositores legati nocuerint.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid putas tu, mi domine et frater, Lutheranos legatos in religionis negotio feliciter acturos?</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scis, quomodo in nostram doctrinam sint affecti; volent omnino locum esse in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> et confessioni <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustanae</placeName>, ex qua ceu ex pixide <persName type="auto_name">Pandore</persName> scis quanta sint per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germaniam</placeName> exorta certamina.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proinde scribo ad d. <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Bezam</persName> et moneo illum in tempore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Te oro, ut literas eas non tantum cures mature, sed tuum quoque adiungas consilium, tuam admonitionem.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De nostrorum pietate nihil dubito; verum scis, quid fiat in tot diversissimorum et astutissimorum comitiis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Foederati nostri 5 cantones tantum non insaniunt contra evangelium; erumpent illi suppetias allaturi <placeName type="auto_name">Guysianis</placeName>, monachis et pfaffis neque retineri aut coherceri poterunt, si modo pecuniae vel stipendia numerentur.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Forte urget ipsos suum illud fatum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Varii sunt apud nos rumores.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proinde liberabis nos sol[l]icitudine anxia, si frequenter, quid in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> fiat, scripseris aut per alios scribi curaveris.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc audimus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglos</placeName> milites festinare in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliam</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam hoc verum sit ac <placeName type="auto_name">Condensis</placeName> partes sequantur!</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas tuas mense hoc scriptas accepimus et maximas tibi pro his agimus gratias.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Prodest nos non imperitos esse rerum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallicarum</placeName>, ut eorum possimus confutare mendatia, qui impensius favent rebus pessimis.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te et symmystas <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyr</persName> et fratres symmystae omnes; saluta tu fratres quoque et symmystas omnes.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus servet te nobis diu incolumem!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri 27. maii 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non relegi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvus sit <persName type="auto_name">Budęus</persName> cum <persName type="auto_name">Jonvilleo</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bullingerus tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Ioanni Calvino</persName>, <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevensis</placeName> ecclesiae fideli ministro, domino colendissimo et fratri charissimo suo.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genff</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
